This button is finished and can be dragged in immediately.

100
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:08,000
Now we will see what happens when we drag this finished button file into the program.

101
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:13,000
It looks like something is happening up over here in the top left corner of our screen, and then out comes your finished buttons.

